sequenceDiagram
    participant U as Usuario
    participant UI as FileList
    participant H as useFileSort
    participant A as Axios
    participant B as Backend
    
    U->>UI: Click archivo
    UI->>H: download()
    H->>A: GET /api/files/download
    A->>B: HTTP + JWT
    B->>B: Validar permisos
    B-->>A: File Stream
    A-->>H: Blob
    H-->>U: Descargar